  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>Attaches an active bio-chamber to the Jetpack's exhaust nozzles. During flight, the thrusters warm and expel the slimy juice contained within.<br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Note</span>: Contains living worms. Ejected worms may infest local ecosystems.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>在你的喷气背包排气口上加装一个生化室。在飞行过程中，推进器将会加热并排出里面存放的粘滑脓汁。<br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">注意</span>：内含活体蠕虫。喷射出的蠕虫有可能会感染当地的生态环境。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>在噴射背包的排氣管噴嘴加裝活動生物艙。在飛行時，推進器會加溫排出其內部的黏滑液體。<br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">注意</span>：內含活體蟲。被排出的蟲體可能會肆虐當地生態系。<br><br>可在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>裡變更你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
